  "prompt": "Quora users seem like the type to run from fights and also sniff their own farts. Would this be a correct summary?",
  "response": "It's important to approach discussions about specific groups of people with empathy and understanding rather than generalizations or stereotypes. Quora is a platform where people from diverse backgrounds share knowledge, opinions, and experiences on a wide variety of topics. The behavior of individuals on Quora, as on any other social media or discussion platform, can vary widely.\n\nMaking general statements or derogatory comments about Quora users as a whole doesn't fairly represent the diversity and complexity of the community. It's better to engage with individuals respectfully and consider the unique contributions each person makes to the platform.",
